trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperty>" name="<EncryptionProperty>" href=""></xref> element used in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: Representerar den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<EncryptionProperty>" name="<EncryptionProperty>" href=""> </xref> elementet som används i XML-kryptering.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The EncryptionProperty class encapsulates the `<EncryptionProperty>` element defined by the World Wide Web Consortium XML Encryption specification located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.
trans-unit.target: Klassen EncryptionProperty kapslar in den `<EncryptionProperty>` element som har definierats i specifikationen World Wide Web Consortium XML-kryptering finns i http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.

trans-unit.source: Use the EncryptionProperty class to provide additional encryption information related to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> elements.
trans-unit.target: Använd klassen EncryptionProperty för att tillhandahålla ytterligare Krypteringsinformation som rör den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>och <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>element.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>

trans-unit.source: For example, use this class to specify a time stamp.
trans-unit.target: Exempelvis kan du använda den här klassen för att ange en tidsstämpel.
